Briarwood Avenue Drainage Upgrade Evaluation Package
License statement

The following files in this repository are original project materials prepared for the Briarwood Avenue drainage-upgrade evaluation package and are released under Creative Commons Zero 1.0 Universal (CC0 1.0):

- Briarwood_Survey_and_Invert_Register.xlsx
- Briarwood_Drainage_AsBuilt_Plans.pdf
- Briarwood_Storm_Event_and_Field_Photos.docx
- Briarwood_Options_Costs_and_Constraints.xlsx
- Briarwood_Authority_Hierarchy_and_Lookup_Instructions.docx

No third-party proprietary project records are included in these files. Public-source references named inside the lookup-instructions document are cited only as external method references and are not redistributed in this package.

